Pan African Resources Boosts Its Barberton Mines Resources Estimate by 7%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-31T08:02:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/pan-african-resources-boosts-its-barberton-mines-resources-estimate-by-7-.html
Pan African Resources Plc (PAF)  said it
increased its total mineral resource estimate at its Barberton
mines operation by 7 percent to 2.55 million ounces of gold.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  